<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"  ng-app="app">
<head >
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no, width=device-width">
    <title>大合麻将</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="lib/angular-carousel.min.css">
    <script src="lib/hammer.js"></script>
    <script src="lib/angular.min.js"></script>
    <script src="lib/angular-carousel.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        angular.module('app',['angular-carousel']).controller('CarouselDemoCtrl',function ($scope,Carousel) {
            $scope.Carousel = Carousel;
        });
    </script>
    <style>
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app"  >
    <div class="flex-1 scroll-y">
        <div class="page-one-main">
            <div style="height: 10px;"></div>
            <div class="logo"></div>
            <div style="height: 10px;"></div>
            <div class="commercial_one"></div>
            <div style="height: 10px;"></div>
            <div class="qc_code"></div>
            <div style="height: 30px;"></div>
            <div class="commercial_two"></div>
            <div class="flex-row" style="height: 50px;">
                <div class="flex-1"></div>
                <div class="android_btn"></div>
                <div class="flex-1"></div>
                <div class="ios_btn"></div>
                <div class="flex-1"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-two-main" style="position: relative" ng-controller="CarouselDemoCtrl">
            <div style="height: 200px;" ng-carousel ng-carousel-name="example-carousel1" ng-carousel-watch="slides">
                <slidecontainer>
                    <slide >
                        <div class="slide_one"></div>
                    </slide>
                    <slide >
                        <div class="slide_two"></div>
                    </slide>
                    <slide >
                        <div class="slide_three"></div>
                    </slide>
                </slidecontainer>
            </div>
            <div style="height: 50px;" class="justify-content-center">
                <div class="flex-row">
                    <div ng-click="Carousel.get('example-carousel1').toIndex($index)"  ng-class="{'icon_point_active':Carousel.get('example-carousel1').currentSlide == $index,'icon_point':Carousel.get('example-carousel1').currentSlide != $index}" ng-repeat="i in [0,1,2]"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="page-three-main">
            <div class="bottom-text-container">
                [ 游戏说明 ] <br>
                <div style="text-indent: 30px;">
                    大合娱乐推出2017年重度力作 '大合麻将' 画面精美，玩法正宗，扣点、推倒胡、风耗子等玩法，更安全，更省流量，更全面，更正宗，大品牌有保证，绝对好玩，绝对刺激，尽在大合麻将。可以和亲朋好友一起游戏，咱山西人最地道的山西麻将。
                </div>
                <br>
                [ 游戏特色 ] <br>
                <div>
                    1，玩法正宗，玩家多，随时随地打开手机就能玩。
                </div>
                <div>
                    2，和好友，亲友和老乡一起畅游。
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>